          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-3">
          <a href="/agent-builder" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-otp-600 font-semibold border-b border-otp-300 hover:text-otp-700 hover:border-otp-600 pb-1">
            Open the builder
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/></svg>
